    "Journal Articles\nMahmudunnabi\nand Zakaria, Muhammad (2014), “Political Factors in the Evolution of Journalism: Comparative Perspectives of the USA, UK and Chinese Journalism,” Journal of Politics and Administration (Peer-reviewed), December 2014,Vol.2, No.1\nDate: 12/01/2014\nMd. Mumit Al Rashid and\nMahmudunnabi\n(2010) “Relations between Ancient India and pre-Islam Iran from historical perspectives”, The Arts Faculty Journal (Peer-reviewed), July 2010, Vol 3, No 4&5, ISSN: 1994-8891, published by the Faculty of Arts, University of Dhaka,\nDate: 07/01/2010",
